e-hostages-release/0000018f-3968-d8fb-a1df-bd6e4c750000</guid></item><item><title>死者家属要求以色列部长和议员不要在阵亡将士纪念日仪式上发言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/bereaved-families-ask-israeli-ministers-mks-not-to-speak-in-memorial-day-ceremonies/0000018f-38f9-d9c3-abcf-7afd943f0000</link><description>以色列议会公布了阵亡将士纪念日仪式的出席名单。极右翼财政部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇 (Bezalel Smotrich) 将于卡法萨巴公墓露面，该公墓埋葬着 10 月 7 日阵亡的以色列士兵罗尼·埃谢尔 (Roni Eshel)。她的父亲说：“我觉得他们似乎是故意伤害我们更多”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 13:31:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/bereaved-families-ask-israeli-ministers-mks-not-to-speak-in-memorial-day-ceremonies/0000018f-38f9-d9c3-abcf-7afd943f0000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫标志性酒吧周六关闭以支持抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/iconic-tel-aviv-bar-shuts-down-on-saturdays-in-support-of-protests/0000018f-3942-d516-afbf-ffc27acb0000</link><description>“我们希望你们也能走上街头。我们不能让政府的失败让我们觉得我们中的任何人都对当前的情况感到满意”，酒吧 Instagram 账户上有一条消息，通知周六晚上的活动停止</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 13:26:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/iconic-tel-aviv-bar-shuts-down-on-saturdays-in-support-of-protests/0000018f-3942-d516-afbf-ffc27acb0000</guid></item><item><title>《兄弟》之前的一切：Netflix 的第一部完全以色列的节目是一次令人困惑的体验</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/television/2024-05-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/anything-before-bros-netflixs-first-fully-israeli-show-is-a-baffling-experience/0000018f-387d-d0b5-a59f-39fd9dd90000</link><description>盖伊·阿米尔和哈南·萨维翁的新剧集是喜剧吗？惊悚片？一部体育戏很少的体育剧？这也引发了一个更大的问题：这部 Netflix 节目到底是为谁准备的？</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 11:08:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/television/2024-05-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/anything-before-bros-netflixs-first-fully-israeli-show-is-a-baffling-experience/0000018f-387d-d0b5-a59f-39fd9dd90000</guid></item><item><title>调查：以色列监视技术和间谍软件出售给印度尼西亚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/investigation-israeli-surveillance-technology-and-spyware-sold-to-indonesia/0000018f-3888-d1f3-a7cf-f9dfa5220000</link><description>国际特赦组织和国土报的联合调查显示，与以色列没有外交关系的印度尼西亚进口了以色列间谍技术。然后新加坡就知道了</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 10:58:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/investigation-israeli-surveillance-technology-and-spyware-sold-to-indonesia/0000018f-3888-d1f3-a7cf-f9dfa5220000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔闯红灯的司机说他在车祸前“悄悄”进入了十字路口</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-driver-who-ran-red-light-says-he-crept-into-the-intersection-before-accident/0000018f-384b-d0b5-a59f-39cf77df0000</link><description>事故发生后，司机受到警方询问，以色列国家安全部长受轻伤。事故中另一名司机的代理律师表示，持有操作许可证驾驶并不意味着交通违法行为得到豁免。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:28:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-driver-who-ran-red-light-says-he-crept-into-the-intersection-before-accident/0000018f-384b-d0b5-a59f-39cf77df0000</guid></item><item><title>这并不是一群不受控制的定居者。这是一次精心策划的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-wasnt-an-uncontrolled-mob-of-settlers-it-was-a-well-orchestrated-assault/0000018f-2e31-d8fb-a1df-af77d3770000</link><description>4 月份，在约旦河西岸的 Al-Mughayyir 村，遭到定居者袭击的巴勒斯坦人中有一个家庭的 30 名成员。他们对那些可怕时刻的描述表明，这绝不是一次自发的袭击</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 08:52:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-wasnt-an-uncontrolled-mob-of-settlers-it-was-a-well-orchestrated-assault/0000018f-2e31-d8fb-a1df-af77d3770000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队使用摩萨德提供的先进机器人在加沙隧道作战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/israeli-army-used-advanced-robots-supplied-by-mossad-for-combat-in-gaza-tunnels/0000018f-3824-d516-afbf-fee630230000</link><description>据报道以色列国家情报机构在战争中行动的情报遗产中心期刊称，军队还配备了先进的面部识别套件，旨在定位恐怖分子和人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 08:21:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/israeli-army-used-advanced-robots-supplied-by-mossad-for-combat-in-gaza-tunnels/0000018f-3824-d516-afbf-fee630230000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反对加沙战争的学生抗议者在哪里？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/where-are-israels-student-protesters-against-the-gaza-war/0000018f-34e7-d0b5-a59f-35e7619c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/where-are-israels-student-protesters-against-the-gaza-war/0000018f-34e7-d0b5-a59f-35e7619c0000</guid></item><item><title>口袋里的 BDS：新应用程序促进抵制在以色列运营的公司</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/bds-in-your-pocket-new-app-promotes-boycott-of-companies-operating-in-israel/0000018f-3410-d0b5-a59f-35d575a00000</link><description>该应用程序“不，谢谢”帮助消费者识别与以色列有联系的全球品牌，尽管一场反攻势已确保该产品在 Google Play 和苹果应用商店上的评分陷入困境</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:04:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/bds-in-your-pocket-new-app-promotes-boycott-of-companies-operating-in-israel/0000018f-3410-d0b5-a59f-35d575a00000</guid></item><item><title>沙特阿拉伯和美国希望达成共同防御协议——无论有没有以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/saudi-arabia-and-the-u-s-want-a-mutual-defense-pact-with-or-without-israel/0000018f-3658-d8fb-a1df-bf7e2e460000</link><description>华盛顿和利雅得担心正常化协议的第三方会以政治利益的名义危及他们的安全利益，因此他们正在制定一项应急计划，根据该计划，双边合作不依赖于以色列与沙特的正常化</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 03:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/saudi-arabia-and-the-u-s-want-a-mutual-defense-pact-with-or-without-israel/0000018f-3658-d8fb-a1df-bf7e2e460000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：任何校园或美国任何地方都不允许反犹太主义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article-live/report-hamas-negative-on-israels-latest-cease-fire-proposal-but-talks-will-continue/0000018f-371f-d0b5-a59f-37df499f0000</link><description>声明称，哈马斯代表团将访问埃及进行停火谈判 ■ 报道：里程碑式的美国和沙特防务协议可能需要数周时间达成 ■ 据彭博社报道，土耳其停止与以色列的所有贸易 ■ 警方开始拆除亲巴勒斯坦示威者营地的路障在加州大学洛杉矶分校</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 02:31:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article-live/report-hamas-negative-on-israels-latest-cease-fire-proposal-but-talks-will-continue/0000018f-371f-d0b5-a59f-37df499f0000</guid></item><item><title>人质家属威胁称，如果协议失败，他们将“围攻”以色列领导人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/families-of-hostages-threaten-to-lay-siege-to-israeli-leaders-if-deal-falls-through/0000018f-362f-d8fb-a1df-bf6ff5870000</link><description>随着人质交易谈判达到紧要关头，抗议活动人士正在加紧斗争</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 22:43:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/families-of-hostages-threaten-to-lay-siege-to-israeli-leaders-if-deal-falls-through/0000018f-362f-d8fb-a1df-bf6ff5870000</guid></item><item><title>以色列监管机构要求不受限制地查阅内塔尼亚胡的战争文件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-watchdog-demands-unrestricted-access-to-netanyahus-war-documents/0000018f-35b8-d8fb-a1df-bdfef19c0000</link><description>国家审计长声称他的办公室仍然“没有得到总理办公室和安全内阁所需的充分合作”</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 21:42:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-watchdog-demands-unrestricted-access-to-netanyahus-war-documents/0000018f-35b8-d8fb-a1df-bdfef19c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方审问人质亲属涉嫌涂鸦并向警察投掷火把</title><